%B0%C6%A1ng/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-ho%E1%BA%A1-ng%E1%BB%B1-ch%E1%BA%BF-K%E1%BB%B3-kh%C3%AD/poem-4kxaLOCIiaYqmROyZjxyBQ">Phụng hoạ ngự chế “Kỳ khí” - 奉和御製奇氣</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-d6YU4KPKjTplShZhxLPIUg">Vũ Dương</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-H%C3%A0m-Ninh/Quy-h%E1%BB%A9ng/poem-pEAEXdglnQQRIVHVfMlzTQ">Quy hứng - 歸興</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-H%C3%A0m-Ninh/author-oTUWo08PVWVgk1Z73UFsZg">Nguyễn Hàm Ninh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/Quy-kh%E1%BB%A9-lai-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-sfHCqxaQ75Zp7Waf7a2TsA">Quy khứ lai từ - 歸去來辭</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/author-y4iJ6v3mYp-Z_KEorcHd_g">Đào Tiềm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-T%C6%B0-Gi%E1%BA%A3n/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-cam/poem-AHD1kB1YgWxrjmiYccNpgg">Thường cam - 嘗甘</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-T%C6%B0-Gi%E1%BA%A3n/author-k2nQ5fnr9ZRE2MDraIsNMQ">Nguyễn Tư Giản</a>)<br></div>	</div>
